A simple example how to use leaflet

You can find nice nice introduction / tutorial at:
https://leafletjs.com/index.html
https://rstudio.github.io/leaflet/
https://allthisblog.wordpress.com/2016/10/12/r-311-with-leaflet-tutorial/
among many others

for our example here, you need to get the csv file "SaenThong_8villages.csv" and the shapefile "SaenThong-rgdal" from training kml file

you can also save your map as a html file, that can be opened with you browser

